{"book": 23, "chapter": 14, "sections": [{"type": "heading", "heading": "從流亡中歸回"}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 1, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華要憐恤雅各，必再揀選以色列，將他們安置在本地。寄居的必與他們聯合，緊貼雅各家。 "}, {"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "外邦人必將他們帶回本土；以色列家必在耶和華的地上得外邦人為僕婢，也要擄掠先前擄掠他們的，轄制先前欺壓他們的。"}]}, {"type": "heading", "heading": "巴比倫王下到陰間"}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "當耶和華使你脫離愁苦、煩惱，並人勉強你做的苦工，得享安息的日子， "}, {"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "你必題這詩歌論巴比倫王說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "欺壓人的何竟熄滅？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "強暴的何竟止息？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 5, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華折斷了惡人的杖，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 5, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "轄制人的圭，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 5, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "就是在忿怒中連連攻擊眾民的，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "在怒氣中轄制列國，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "行逼迫無人阻止的。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "現在全地得安息，享平靜；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "人皆發聲歡呼。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "松樹和黎巴嫩的香柏樹"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "都因你歡樂，說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "自從你仆倒，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "再無人上來砍伐我們。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "你下到陰間，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "陰間就因你震動來迎接你，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "又因你驚動在世曾為首領的陰魂，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "並使那曾為列國君王的，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "都離位站起。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "他們都要發言對你說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "你也變為軟弱像我們一樣嗎？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "你也成了我們的樣子嗎？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 11, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "你的威勢和你琴瑟的聲音都下到陰間。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 11, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "你下鋪的是蟲，上蓋的是蛆。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 11, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "明亮之星，早晨之子啊，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "你何竟從天墜落？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "你這攻敗列國的何竟被砍倒在地上？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "你心裏曾說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "我要升到天上；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "我要高舉我的寶座在神眾星以上；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "我要坐在聚會的山上，在北方的極處。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "我要升到高雲之上；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "我要與至上者同等。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "然而，你必墜落陰間，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "到坑中極深之處。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "凡看見你的都要定睛看你，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "留意看你，說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "使大地戰抖，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "使列國震動，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 17, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "使世界如同荒野，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 17, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "使城邑傾覆，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 17, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "不釋放被擄的人歸家，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 17, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "是這個人嗎？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 17, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 18, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "列國的君王"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 18, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "俱各在自己陰宅的榮耀中安睡。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 18, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 19, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "惟獨你被拋棄，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 19, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "不得入你的墳墓，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 19, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "好像可憎的枝子，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 19, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "以被殺的人為衣，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 19, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "就是被刀刺透，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 19, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "墜落坑中石頭那裏的；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 19, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "你又像被踐踏的屍首一樣。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 19, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 20, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "你不得與君王同葬；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 20, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "因為你敗壞你的國，殺戮你的民。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 20, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "惡人後裔的名，必永不提說。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 20, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 21, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "先人既有罪孽，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 21, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "就要預備殺戮他的子孫，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 21, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "免得他們興起來，得了遍地，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 21, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "在世上修滿城邑。"}]}, {"type": "heading", "heading": "神要毀滅巴比倫"}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 21, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 22, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "萬軍之耶和華說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 22, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "我必興起攻擊他們，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 22, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "將巴比倫的名號和所餘剩的人，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 22, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "連子帶孫一併剪除。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 22, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "這是耶和華說的。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 22, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "我必使巴比倫為箭豬所得，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "又變為水池；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "我要用滅亡的掃帚掃淨它。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "這是萬軍之耶和華說的。"}]}, {"type": "heading", "heading": "神要毀滅亞述"}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 24, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "萬軍之耶和華起誓說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 24, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "我怎樣思想，必照樣成就；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 24, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "我怎樣定意，必照樣成立，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 24, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 25, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "就是在我地上打折亞述人，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 25, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "在我山上將他踐踏。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 25, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他加的軛必離開以色列人；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 25, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他加的重擔必離開他們的肩頭。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 25, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 26, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "這是向全地所定的旨意；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 26, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "這是向萬國所伸出的手。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 26, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 27, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "萬軍之耶和華既然定意，誰能廢棄呢？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 27, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他的手已經伸出，誰能轉回呢？"}]}, {"type": "heading", "heading": "神要毀滅非利士"}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 27, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 28, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 亞哈斯王崩的那年，就有以下的默示："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 28, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 29, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 非利士全地啊，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 29, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "不要因擊打你的杖折斷就喜樂。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 29, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "因為從蛇的根必生出毒蛇；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 29, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "牠所生的是火焰的飛龍。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 29, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 30, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "貧寒人的長子必有所食；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 30, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "窮乏人必安然躺臥。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 30, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "我必以饑荒治死你的根；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 30, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "你所餘剩的人必被殺戮。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 30, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 31, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "門哪，應當哀號！"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 31, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "城啊，應當呼喊！"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 31, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " 非利士全地啊，你都消化了！"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 31, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "因為有煙從北方出來，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 31, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他行伍中並無亂隊的。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 31, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 32, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "可怎樣回答外邦的使者呢？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 32, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "必說：耶和華建立了錫安；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 32, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他百姓中的困苦人必投奔在其中。"}]}]}